* NFStream also extracts [**60+ flow statistical features**][stat_feat]

```python
from nfstream import NFStreamer
my_awesome_streamer = NFStreamer(source="facebook.pcap", statistics=True)
for flow in my_awesome_streamer:
    print(flow)
```

